1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about El Nino than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:09,200
El Nino is a complex climate pattern that affects weather worldwide.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:13,600
It involves warmer ocean temperatures in the Pacific, altering wind patterns.

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:18,800
This can lead to heavier rains in some areas and droughts in others.

5
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:22,800
Understanding El Nino helps us prepare for its unpredictable effects.

6
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:25,600
